text: The Man from Utah is a 1934 American western movie directed by Robert N. Bradbury and starring John Wayne, Polly Anne Young, Yakima Canutt, George Cleveland. It was distributed by Monogram Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1934 movies Category:1930s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Robert N.
